messages.content: Hey there! This is EZ Mobile Mechanic. What's going on with your vehicle?
Hey! What’s up with your vehicle?
I didn't catch that. What's going on with your vehicle?
up and down on the side of the road
Gotcha! Can you tell me the year, make, and model of your vehicle?
Cool, what make and model is it? And what's the issue?
all right it's a make the make is F-150 know it's a Ford
Perfect, so a 95 Ford F-150. What's going on with it?
is I'm broken down on the side of the road I think it overheated
Oh no, sorry to hear that! I’ll get you set up. Do you want me to text you an estimate for the repair?
I'll have someone call you right back. Thanks for calling!
